ygData.messageBody:
Found this on everlore: (www.everlore.com)Slaying of

Nagafen on Karana
Shan'tell [10/8/99 1:21:42 AM PST]
I am proud to announce that last night (10-6-99) my
guild has slain Nagafen. Our group consisted of 10
level 50 adventurers, 3 wizards, 2 clerics, a ranger, 2
warriors and 2 monks. I have been informed that this
was the first time a group has slain Nagafen in under 5
minutes with such a group so few in numbers.

Nagafen's quickly decomposing body wielded red dragon
scales, a cloak of flames, blight hammer of scourge and
the rune of frost.
